## Context

Add a new Prisma generator package to the monorepo that reads a Prisma schema's DMMF and outputs a single `client.ts` file containing TypeScript interfaces, string-union enum types, per-model `*Resource` classes (with typed CRUD methods over `fetch`), and a top-level `RestApiClient` class that composes all resource accessors.

